<item>
  <title><![CDATA[学习资源]]></title>
  <description><![CDATA[
<div class="post-date"> Posted: 2020-06-03</div>
<div id="outline-container-orgab1b3b2" class="outline-2">
<h2 id="orgab1b3b2">Emacs</h2>
<div class="outline-text-2" id="text-orgab1b3b2">
</div>
<div id="outline-container-orgd8ea8c6" class="outline-3">
<h3 id="orgd8ea8c6">Emacs Org-mode - a system for note-taking and project planning (2008)</h3>
<div class="outline-text-3" id="text-orgd8ea8c6">
<p>
Carsten Dominik - Org-mode 的作者，在 Google Tech Talk 上的做得演示，可以了解到Org-mode的一些想法。 <br>
<a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=oJTwQvgfgMM">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=oJTwQvgfgMM</a>
</p>
</div>
</div>

<div id="outline-container-org9168efc" class="outline-3">
<h3 id="org9168efc">The Emacs Ipython Notebook- John Miller (Honeywell UOP)</h3>
<div class="outline-text-3" id="text-org9168efc">
<p>
John Miller - EIN(emacs ipython notebook) 现在的 maintainer， 分享 ein 作为一个 jupyter 前端 与 Emacs <br>
结合的体验。 <br>
<a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=OB9vFu9Za8w">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=OB9vFu9Za8w</a>
</p>
</div>
</div>

<div id="outline-container-orgece8036" class="outline-3">
<h3 id="orgece8036">Conquering Kubernetes with Emacs</h3>
<div class="outline-text-3" id="text-orgece8036">
<p>
用 org-mode 做的 live coding 现场演示, 用 Emacs Lisp 写了个 kubernetes gui 客户端 <br>
看完后，对 org-mode 文学编程方面会有更深的了解，同时对 Emacs 的强大有个直观的了解 <br>
<a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=w3krYEeqnyk">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=w3krYEeqnyk</a>
</p>
</div>
</div>

<div id="outline-container-org48b01a4" class="outline-3">
<h3 id="org48b01a4">It's Magit! - John Wiegley</h3>
<div class="outline-text-3" id="text-org48b01a4">
<p>
Emacs 杀手级应用 Magit，你值得拥有 <br>
<a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=j-k-lkilbEs">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=j-k-lkilbEs</a>
</p>
</div>
</div>

<div id="outline-container-orgafd811d" class="outline-3">
<h3 id="orgafd811d">Using Emacs Episode 67 - An Emacs vs Vim rant</h3>
<div class="outline-text-3" id="text-orgafd811d">
<p>
Mike Zamansky 的 Using Emacs 系列，这不是一个emacs与vim引战的视频，而是非常客观地展示了编辑器的历史和演进过程 <br>
这里的展示就是字面意思，把历史上的编辑器捞出来用给你们看:) <br>
<a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=0M6erlK57go">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=0M6erlK57go</a>
</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>

<div id="outline-container-org4303b31" class="outline-2">
<h2 id="org4303b31">Linux Documentation Project Guides</h2>
<div class="outline-text-2" id="text-org4303b31">
<p>
<a href="https://tldp.org/guides.html">https://tldp.org/guides.html</a>
</p>
</div>

<div id="outline-container-orgeecad78" class="outline-3">
<h3 id="orgeecad78">GNU/Linux Command-Line Tools Summary</h3>
<div class="outline-text-3" id="text-orgeecad78">
<p>
介绍 Linux 下常用的命令行工具 <br>
<a href="https://tldp.org/guides.html#gnu-tools">https://tldp.org/guides.html#gnu-tools</a>
</p>
</div>
</div>

<div id="outline-container-orgae1bda9" class="outline-3">
<h3 id="orgae1bda9">Bash Guide for Beginners</h3>
<div class="outline-text-3" id="text-orgae1bda9">
<p>
介绍 Bash 脚本 <br>
<a href="https://tldp.org/guides.html#bbg">https://tldp.org/guides.html#bbg</a>
</p>
</div>
</div>

<div id="outline-container-orga595e0e" class="outline-3">
<h3 id="orga595e0e">Advanced Bash-Scripting Guide</h3>
<div class="outline-text-3" id="text-orga595e0e">
<p>
Bash 工具书，需要时再查看 <br>
<a href="https://tldp.org/guides.html#abs">https://tldp.org/guides.html#abs</a>
</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>

<div id="outline-container-orgc5dc7fc" class="outline-2">
<h2 id="orgc5dc7fc">Standord CS 253 Web Security</h2>
<div class="outline-text-2" id="text-orgc5dc7fc">
<p>
斯坦福CS253网络安全，通过网络攻防，了解HTTP(s)协议、跨域、跨站脚本攻击、浏览器安全机制等等 <br>
课上ppt、live coding、课后作业都很不错 <br>
<a href="https://web.stanford.edu/class/cs253/">https://web.stanford.edu/class/cs253/</a>
</p>
</div>
</div>

<div id="outline-container-orgb96278f" class="outline-2">
<h2 id="orgb96278f">Build XXX from scratch</h2>
<div class="outline-text-2" id="text-orgb96278f">
<p>
麻雀虽小，五脏俱全
</p>
</div>

<div id="outline-container-org77c82ec" class="outline-3">
<h3 id="org77c82ec">Build Your Own Text Editor</h3>
<div class="outline-text-3" id="text-org77c82ec">
<p>
1000行C代码手把手写一个简单的终端编辑器，蛮有意思的，从重可以了解到一些ASCII, VT100 Escape sequence&#x2026;处理方式 <br>
<a href="https://viewsourcecode.org/snaptoken/kilo/index.html">https://viewsourcecode.org/snaptoken/kilo/index.html</a>
</p>
</div>
</div>

<div id="outline-container-org7e834be" class="outline-3">
<h3 id="org7e834be">Let's Build a Simple Database</h3>
<div class="outline-text-3" id="text-org7e834be">
<p>
Writing a sqlite clone from scratch in C <br>
<a href="https://cstack.github.io/db_tutorial/">https://cstack.github.io/db_tutorial/</a>
</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
